Achievements.Name: I'm With Iron Man
Achievements.Description: Defeat all Act II and III missions as a Pro-Registration team.

Achievements.Name: I'm With Captain America
Achievements.Description: Defeat all Act II and III missions as an Anti-Registration team.

Achievements.Name: Legendary Schism
Achievements.Description: Defeat all Act I missions on Legendary Difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Legendary War
Achievements.Description: Defeat all Act II missions on Legendary Difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Legendary Alliance
Achievements.Description: Defeat all Act III missions on Legendary Difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Uncontained Aggression
Achievements.Description: You or other players on your team must destroy 250 health containers.

Achievements.Name: Undefeated Heroes
Achievements.Description: Defeat 12 mission bosses on Super Heroic or Legendary Difficulty without revival or map reload.

Achievements.Name: Immortal Heroics
Achievements.Description: Defeat 25 maps on Super Heroic or Legendary Difficulty without revival or map reload.

Achievements.Name: Tactical Training
Achievements.Description: Perform all 5 recommended training Fusions in Latveria.

Achievements.Name: Heroes Unite
Achievements.Description: Perform 10 Fusions with another player-controlled hero in a Co-Op game.

Achievements.Name: United We Stand
Achievements.Description: Earn 20 high scores for each type of Fusion: Targeted, Guided, and Clearing.

Achievements.Name: Powers of Two
Achievements.Description: Perform all Fusions by combining every available pairing of 24 heroes.

Achievements.Name: Old Friends
Achievements.Description: Have 10 special conversations between characters with a history while in an HQ map.

Achievements.Name: Potential Evidence
Achievements.Description: Collect 10 Concept Art Bundles in HQ maps.

Achievements.Name: Sim Team-Up
Achievements.Description: Earn Mission Succeeded on a Simulator Mission in Co-Op and return to the Simulator menu.

Achievements.Name: Sim Amateur
Achievements.Description: Earn 4 Bronze Medals from Simulator Missions.

Achievements.Name: Sim Expert
Achievements.Description: Earn 8 Silver Medals from Simulator Missions.

Achievements.Name: Sim Champion
Achievements.Description: Earn 12 Gold Medals from Simulator Missions.

Achievements.Name: Melee Training
Achievements.Description: Complete all melee training goals listed on the Stats page.

Achievements.Name: Power Training
Achievements.Description: Complete all Power training goals listed on the Stats page.

Achievements.Name: Every Trick in the Book
Achievements.Description: Complete all combat mastery goals listed on the Stats page.
